snippet.title: Onward | Gaming Showcase Trailer - Update 1.11 | Meta Quest
snippet.description:
Play Onward: https://metaque.st/3MhHoIO 

Update 1.11 will be available this summer and is bringing some much requested changes to the game. Including major updates to features such as new player animations, redesigned game lobby (tent) environment, and revisions to the shooting range. In addition, we will be releasing two new weapons, the M240L & Ultimax. There will also be a variety of system improvements to enhance the players overall experience when playing. More details will be shared as time gets closer to launch.
